          { "speaker": "Vendeuse", "text": "Il coûte quatre-vingt-quinze euros.", "translation": "It costs ninety-five euros." },
          { "speaker": "Client", "text": "C'est un peu cher... Vous avez une réduction ?", "translation": "That's a bit expensive... Do you have a discount?" },
          { "speaker": "Vendeuse", "text": "Oui, moins vingt pour cent aujourd'hui.", "translation": "Yes, minus twenty percent today." }
